    General Stores in Bandra East, Mumbai

    (367 Ratings & Reviews) 4.0 Average Ratings

    General Stores in Bandra East, Mumbai

    Commonly known as 'kiranas' in the local parlance, mom-n-pop shops are nothing but general stores. In marketing terminology, a kirana shop is a form of traditional retail catering to the needs of citizens. Now with the emergence of the various forms of modern retail, many of these establishments are evolving from its traditional format to a more modern, department store format. These shops and establishments are a part of the distributor network of FMCG brands and companies selling a wide range of products. The vast list of general store items does not limit to food grains, pulses, household items, toiletries, cosmetics, biscuits and packaged food items, bakery products, confectionery items, and local foods. Catering to the convenience of their customers, these shops also extend free home delivery service. Aiming for the convenience of the locals, these general stores also offer complimentary doorstep delivery services. You can find one from a large number of General Stores in Bandra East, Mumbai from the list given above.
